        "code": "/**\n * {@inheritDoc}. This basically clears all the markers, the\n * initialFive list and sets countOfObservations to 0.\n */\n@Override\npublic void clear() {\n    markers = null;\n    initialFive.clear();\n    countOfObservations = 0L;\n    pValue = Double.NaN;\n}"
