        "code": "/**\n * {@inheritDoc}\n */\n@Override\npublic double getResult() {\n    if (Double.compare(quantile, 1d) == 0) {\n        pValue = maximum();\n    } else if (Double.compare(quantile, 0d) == 0) {\n        pValue = minimum();\n    }\n    return pValue;\n}"
